{"tid":2183983,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"不稱職的法官- 古德明","createTime":"2020-09-01T09:11:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-01T10:21:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6724c0cea4122d1b51230cbd0b863b20de4fc2af","tid":2183983,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T09:11:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200901/5ARF4XRPQ5DXTNOIP3NQJK2IMI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200901%2F5ARF4XRPQ5DXTNOIP3NQJK2IMI%2F&d=X54jjuw0UQFZuhWzkrVO7mzUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=3eaba598\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200901%2F5ARF4XRPQ5DXTNOIP3NQJK2IMI%2F&h=419d9a1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200901/5ARF4XRPQ5DXTNOIP3NQJK2IMI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n不稱職的法官- 古德明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RwP2rWN8HGG7qqUZldzE9B3BNTo=/1183x839/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZJRNYVVP2FEPXBDXU2PWLBAYDQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRwP2rWN8HGG7qqUZldzE9B3BNTo%3D%2F1183x839%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZJRNYVVP2FEPXBDXU2PWLBAYDQ.png&h=c33951bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n八月中旬，去年民變期間兩宗案件定讞，頗足顯示香港公安的質素。第一宗是北角區議員仇栩欣案。根據現場錄影，兩名公安見仇栩欣在拍攝他們「維持治安」的手段，上前冷冷問道：「拍完了沒有？」他們隨即出手，襲擊仇栩欣，把她推倒地上，膝壓其身，手扼其頸，最後還控告她「襲警」。怪不得裁判官何俊堯判仇栩欣無罪，還指出：「警察與市民說話，態度怎麼這樣輕佻？兩名警察根本不是在正當執行職務，用武也不得其宜，還謊話連篇。當局應記錄在案。」<br />\n<br />\n另一宗是工程師陳俊賢「管有攻擊用武器」案。兩名公安上庭作證，一個說看見陳俊賢「背着黑色背囊，拿着黑色手提包」，另一個則說看見何俊堯「手提包從背囊裏掉出來，裏面有電鑽、鐵鎚等等」，而證物則是個橙色背囊。怪不得裁判官何俊堯判陳俊賢無罪之餘，批評兩名公安說：「證人所言不合理，前後矛盾，證物也可疑得很。」<br />\n<br />\n《昨非庵日纂．宦澤》載：。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n不過，何俊堯這樣的法官，。。。。。。"},{"pid":"14197a9f2e34b450f1894b757796a0547acef8f2","tid":2183983,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-01T10:21:01.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}